_sText:
This is a GunGame Map i made when i was bored :D
You can also play it as a usual map, as there are buyzones, but
they get removed if GunGame is turned on.

Credits go out to Boharox for the Lego Textures.

The custom textures are in the .bsp, so you dont need to
download the textures on your own.

Have Fun !


PS: Sry for any spelling mistakes you can find, im from germany :D
